com.evolup.test.IAPTest01.util

Class IabException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • com.evolup.test.IAPTest01.util.IabException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class IabException
extends Exception
    Exception thrown when something went wrong with in-app billing. An IabException has an associated IabResult (an error). To get the IAB result that caused this exception to be thrown, call getResult().
